\begin_inset Formula $0\le i\le r+1$
\end_inset

 и 
\begin_inset Formula $0\le j\le s+1$
\end_inset

, тогда 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sigma\left(nm\right)=\sum_{i=0}^{r+1}\sum_{j=0}^{s+1}d_{i}g_{j}.
\]

\end_inset

 Так как 
\begin_inset Formula $d_{i}$
\end_inset

